-- MOVES-NAPF appoints Mike Weston as CEO of PIP Ltd 
-- 
-- Mon Sep 22, 2014 07:47AM EDT
-- None



Sept 22 (Reuters) - The National Association of Pension Funds said it appointed Mike Weston chief executive of the Pensions Infrastructure Platform Ltd, effective immediately.

Weston has worked as the in-house chief investment officer at DMGT Plc <DMGOa.L> pension schemes.